TextEng: Yes. My name is <FirstName>. What do you need?
I might be. Why do you ask?
Text: 그럴 수도 있죠. 왜 묻는 거예요?

TextEng: Yes. Me be <FirstName>. How me help you?
I don't like attacking animals, so what am I supposed to do about it?
Text: 동물들을 공격하는 건 싫은데, 어떻게 해야 하죠?

TextEng: What can I do to be of assistance?
That doesn't really interest me right now.
Me no like hurt animals. What me do about it?
Text: 나 동물 다치게 하는 거 싫어. 나 뭐 해야 돼?

TextEng: I guess I should go check it out then.
Where is the Neverwinter Wood from here?
I'm really not interested. Thanks anyway.
Me go see what me can do there.
Text: 나 가서 뭐 할 수 있는지 볼게.

TextEng: Me not want to do that. Bye bye.
Text: 나 그거 하고 싶지 않아. 안녕.

TextEng: What were you needing help with again?
I don't need any supplies, thanks.
I would like to see your wares.
